a92ee83 [cli] Follow symlinks in plugin or theme completions - a280726 [fossil] Refactor `fossil_prompt_info` and quote % in branch - dfaad77 [helm] Fix completion loading mechanism - a0a949d [installer] Fix `sudo` check for users with password or without privileges - b7a59e6 [installer] Run `chsh` with sudo if user has privileges - e7390a8 [jenv] Quote % in `jenv_prompt_info` - 4f2d8b4 [kubectl] Source completion instead of autoloading it - 31d63ea [kubectx] Allow prompt sequences in `kubectx_mapping` (#10562) - d87ab25 [kubectx] Quote % in `kubectx_prompt_info` - 304af0a [lib] Quote % in `git_remote_status` - 5b076ea [lib] Quote % in `nvm_prompt_info` - aaebe4c [mvn] Fix listing modules in completion (#10586) - 42afa6e [pyenv] Quote % in `pyenv_prompt_info` - c6e7f89 [rust] Fix `cargo` completion when sysroot contains spaces (#10571) - 71e6d5f [svn] Fix output order in `svn_dirty_choose` (#10572) - 1e27755 [svn] Fix sed call in `svn_get_rev_nr` (#10590) - 93ec48f [svn] Refactor and quote % characters in `svn_prompt_info` - c76dc91 [svn] Return true repo name in `svn_get_repo_name` - 75ed59b [svn-fast-info] Quote % characters in svn branch name - ef3a85c [svn-fast-info] URL-decode svn branch name - 4e777ef [trapd00r] Fix potential command injection in `zsh_path` - a7c46d0 [ubuntu] Fix `defining function based on alias` error (#10560) - 805427e [updater] Give priority to `zstyle` settings if set (#10587) - 3e9fe6e [virtualenv] Quote % in `virtualenv_prompt_info` - 93cea53 [yarn] Update completion (#10579)
Documentation:
- 4e2f4cd [vi-mode] Fix link typo in readme (#10570)
Other changes:
- d3bb52d Style: Declare globals properly - 67cc59b Style: Some code style fixes - fbdc078 Style: Use 24bit colors in Oh My Zsh logo if supported - 567bd59 [cli] Refactor: Use self-referencing in subcommand functions - c63ba17 [installer] Refactor: Simplify `user_can_sudo` check - 7ae4f76 [kubectl] Refactor: Optimize completion generation - 596cef8 [svn-fast-info] Style: Fix code style and `svn info` locale - bddecfe [updater] Style: Remove statl from `git pull`
